ReturnPolicy.Description:
Domestic Policy: Most unopened items in new condition and returned within 30 days from the ship date will receive a refund or exchange. Items purchased between 11/1-12/25 may be returned up to 60 days from the ship date.  Items that are opened or damaged or do not have a packing slip or receipt may be denied a refund or exchange. Most purchases can be returned to a U.S. Target store, just bring in your item and the packing slip that came with it to the Guest Service Desk for a refund or exchange. All Paypal purchased items that are returned to a Target store will be refunded to cash.  If you choose to mail in your items, please call us at 612-307-8330 or click Contact Us on the Target storefront page, and we will help you return your item to our Return Center.  You will receive a refund to your Paypal account once the product has been received and processed (usually within 7-10 days from the day we receive your return). Target does not currently offer exchanges through the mail return process, but you may exchange for a similar item at any U.S. Target store.

International Policy:  Items returned within 30 days from the ship date or 28 days of delivery (whichever is the latest) will receive a refund. Items purchased between 1 November and 15 January, may be returned up to 60 days from the ship date.  To return your items, please call us at 1- 612-307-8330, email us at ebay.sales@target.com, or click 'Contact Us' on the Target storefront page, and we will help you return your item to our Return Center (please allow an additional day for response due to time zone differences).  You will receive a refund to your PayPal account no later than 14 days from the day we receive your return at our returns facility or you provide evidence of returned goods. Target does not currently offer exchanges through the mail return process. Buyer is responsible for return shipping expense and is required to fill out all necessary customs paperwork prior to shipping. U.S Target stores cannot accept international returns or exchanges, including international returns and exchanges of online purchases.
